text: Daniel Morys (born 26 December 2000), is a Polish professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Olimpia Elbląg on loan from Wisła Kraków. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Polish footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Wisła Kraków players Category:Olimpia Elbląg players Category:Ekstraklasa players
